00:02:34.710 --> 00:02:35.350
Ling,

00:02:35.750 --> 00:02:36.350
yo...

00:02:36.640 --> 00:02:37.560
¿Lo quieres o no?

00:02:41.590 --> 00:02:42.120
Sí, quiero.

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:43.510
Gracias, Ling.

00:02:48.560 --> 00:02:49.200
Esta pregunta

00:02:49.950 --> 00:02:50.790
