00:03:56.120 --> 00:03:56.750
¿Qué pretendes hacer?

00:03:56.840 --> 00:03:57.590
Yo no...

00:03:57.710 --> 00:03:58.310
Bien,

00:03:58.750 --> 00:03:59.520
