00:07:11.870 --> 00:07:12.750
que conocía antes.

00:07:13.630 --> 00:07:14.310
O tal vez

00:07:15.240 --> 00:07:16.070
llévala a visitar los lugares

00:07:16.190 --> 00:07:17.190
